---
title: Mexican Style Cheeseburger with Loaded Chorizo Sweet Potato Fries, Chipotle Mayo and Salad
description: This Mexican Style Cheeseburger is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-style-cheeseburger-7bc3c4e2-0a5077fe.jpg
